{"tid":2013364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尋人 有無人係「柯__輝」嘅親人/朋友","createTime":"2020-05-12T09:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T04:56:28.000Z","uid":34061,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"6add480cf66fbe6587a1efb0041c332afab9bed7","tid":2013364,"uid":34061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T09:01:29.000Z","msg":"我係5/10大圍捕 其中一個被鳩拉嘅街坊 <br />\n入面有個小朋友 13歲 id: s086xxx (9)搜到丫叉 鋼珠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入多條非法管有違禁品xx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見佢好驚 同 唔知點算 好擔心有無人幫佢<br />\n今日晏就先保出黎 見佢都未錄口供 千叮萬囑左佢要無野講 希望佢做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聯絡左星火 未覆 <br />\n有無人識佢 報個平安"},{"pid":"de5d5a597ad75680498100aa5b142fdfa1300fe9","tid":2013364,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T09:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d438522a08323e921062b8128e04d712c856fc42","tid":2013364,"uid":8014,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T09:05:43.000Z","msg":"幫你推左先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 可唔可以叫啲小朋友唔好再玩啲低成效高成本嘅野<br />\n<br />\ne.g. 丫叉 laser pen <br />\n<br />\n一條狗毛都傷唔到 遇到紅官又要坐幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750ef1fef1e428496740b119e04fa59a2c0d1ab5","tid":2013364,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T09:07:23.000Z","msg":"有冇通知被捕人士關注組"},{"pid":"fc085e4ccb666b15d9aefffc914ded50811faeb3","tid":2013364,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T09:08:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"72268d766c0b27fc3cad6598c3bf1d796b4c97a9","tid":2013364,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T09:08:12.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid"